long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Address book for Q blockchain community members.

Features:
- Add your friends to your contacts
- Manage contacts list
- Export/Import contacts (JSON file)
- Display your contacts in Your HQ
